# How to reinstall VM for ColossusCloud

For reinstalling VM for ColossusCloud, please do the following steps:

- Login to client portal from https://portal.serverpoint.com/cgi-bin/gen4cp/engine/login.cgi
- Click "Manage your Vms" 
- Click "Settings of the VM" you need
- Click "Actions" and click "Reinstall"
- Select the OS from the "Available OS templates" drop down.
- Click "Reinstall Operating System"
